outputs.output_descr: Project will build capacity of the newly established State Directorate on Rehabilitation and Further Development of Osh and Jalal-Abad cities and support it in development of general plans of two cities, the Early Recovery Strategy and its Action Plan.

project_descr: Capacity building of the State Directorate for early recovery post-crisis needs assessment, recovery planning and restoration of Osh and Jalal-Abad cities of the Kyrgyz Republic
project_title: Capacity building of the State Directorate
